data.description:
Rare Opportunity Alert! Step into the home of your dreams with a financial advantage - an assumable VA loan at an incredible rate of 4.375%! Ideal for those seeking both a beautiful residence and a savvy investment, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and cost-effectiveness.

Nestled within a sprawling 35-acre estate, this exquisite property offers a serene and private lifestyle. The house boasts four generously sized bedrooms, two well-appointed bathrooms, and the luxury of walk-in closets in three of the four bedrooms, ensuring ample storage and convenience.

The heart of the home is the open-plan living area, where large windows frame stunning views of the surrounding nature, bringing in an abundance of natural light. The kitchen, equipped with modern appliances, is perfect for culinary enthusiasts.

Outdoors, the property includes two detached massive six-car garage outbuildings plus a 10 x 16 storage shed attached to one of the garages. The attached shed has been isolated. 

The land itself offers endless possibilities, whether outdoor recreation, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your own vast, private space. This is more than a home; it's a retreat for those who appreciate peace, space, and nature.
